{"comments":"Curves Effect — Industry-standard bezier curve color correction.\n\n## Industry Standard\n\nMirrors AE's Curves effect with per-channel bezier curves:\n\n- **Master curve**: Applies to all RGB channels (luminance)\n- **Red/Green/Blue curves**: Per-channel adjustment\n- **Alpha curve**: Alpha channel adjustment\n\nEach curve is defined by control points with optional bezier handles.\n\n## Curve Points\n\n| Property | Type | Min | Max | Notes |\n|----------|------|-----|-----|-------|\n| x (input) | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | Input value |\n| y (output) | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | Output value |\n| handleInX | Number | - | - | Bezier handle in (relative) |\n| handleInY | Number | - | - | Bezier handle in (relative) |\n| handleOutX | Number | - | - | Bezier handle out (relative) |\n| handleOutY | Number | - | - | Bezier handle out (relative) |\n\nMinimum 2 points per curve (start and end). Default is linear (no adjustment).\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["x",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Percentage"],"Ratio"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["y",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Percentage"],"Ratio"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["handleInX",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["handleInY",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["handleOutX",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["handleOutY",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/Curves.purs","start":[104,27]},"title":"CurveControlPoint"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Effects","ColorCorrection","Curves"],"CurveControlPoint"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[113,60],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/Curves.purs","start":[113,1]},"title":"eqCurveControlPoint"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Effects","ColorCorrection","Curves"],"CurveControlPoint"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[117,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/Curves.purs","start":[115,1]},"title":"showCurveControlPoint"}],"comments":"Control point on a curve with optional bezier handles.\n\nX = input value (0.0-1.0), Y = output value (0.0-1.0).\nHandles are relative to the point position (unbounded).\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan